Unity Pricing Structure:
"how will this affect me longterm?"

FREE:
	you can build whatever you want freely and publish (you need the logo)
	you only get the lame skin for unity-editor
	server allows 20 playeres at a time

Plus:
	server allows 50 players mutliplayer at a time
	$35/seat
	cool skins
	no splash screen!

Pro:
	200 players at a time for free and you can buy more and get price quotes etc

BITGEM - buying assets, they're expensive but you get 15% off with the code:
	mark_price_unity_3d_course

	not bad!
